changeLogMessages: Fix a bug where calling GetBucketIntelligentTiering with no IntelligentTieringId would call ListBucketIntelligentTieringConfigurations. Now, calling GetBucketIntelligentTiering with no IntelligentTieringId will throw an exception.
[Breaking Change] IsSetIntelligentTieringConfigurationList() on ListBucketIntelligentTieringConfigurationsResponse changed from public to internal to follow other IsSet methods.
